description: From Cree ᒥᓵᐢᑿᑑᒥᐣ (misaaskwatoomin, “saskatoon berry”), from ᒥᓵᐢᑿᐟ (misaaskwat, “saskatoon shrub”) + ᒥᐣ (min, “berry”), from Proto-Algonquian *miškwat- ("exchange, trade"), Proto-Algonquian *mini.

entries.meaning: (Canadian Prairies) A shrub inhabiting western North America, Amelanchier alnifolia.
(Canadian Prairies) The edible berry of this shrub.
